.com/80/v2-3e928101ac9d419c626d05b6275ee2c5_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/625750958"}}, "attached_info": "CkAItbWlrrr8wplLEAMaCTEwMTMzNDgyOSCTn52pBjAAOMQFQApyCTYyNTc1MDk1OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1697249482.448729", "card_id": "Q_625918067", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 265}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "以色列工人银行估算「此次战争成本将至少达 68 亿美元」，这一金额意味着什么？战争将如何影响全球经济？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "巴以冲突到 13 日满一周，以色列一些人开始算经济账。根据以色列第一大银行工人银行的粗略估计，此次战争的成本将至少达 68 亿美元。 美国 CNBC 网站 12 日报道称，自冲突爆发以来，以色列国防军征召了超过 30 万名预备役军人执行任务，这一数字是前所未有的。这些预备役军人来自各行各业，有教师、科技工作者、创业者、农民、律师、医生、旅游业从业者和工人等。他们脱离日常经济生产活动，投入战斗。以色列希伯来大学经济学教授埃亚尔·温特表示，以色列经济损失的大小将取决于这些预备役人员离开工作岗位的时间，时间越久对该国经济的打击也就越大。温特称，受战争的影响，以色列旅游业会立即衰退。（环球时报）冲突一周！以色列工人银行估算：战争成本将至少达 68 亿美元"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-15166a95f9275330361618eb05b9e96c_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/625918067"}}, "attached_info": "CkAItbWlrrr8wplLEAMaCTEwMTM3MTkxMyCD0KKpBjAAOL0EQAtyCTYyNTkxODA2N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1697249482.449463", "card_id": "Q_400594636", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 206}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "什么叫无效社交？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-42cefc313d2d5702d8054641704ade4d.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https